Nomzamo Yuku Ventura Street in Factreton where the fatal shooting took place. (Supplied) Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories A 14-year-old boy has been shot dead in Ventura Street in Factreton this morning (Wednesday 21 June). According to the community he was caught in the crossfire of the ongoing shooting in the area. They say more than 20 gun shots were heard this morning and the body of the teenage boy was found lying in the street. The secretary of the Community Policing Forum, Cheslyn Steenberg, confirmed the incident. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.